window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>My forbidden husband.</b></p> <p>I kissed my father’s best friend, and it kind of didn’t go well.</p> <p>Not only because he’s 18 years older than me - but he also didn’t like it. Not one bit.</p> <p>In my defense, I didn’t mean to fall for him. It just happened.</p> <p>Nathaniel Weaver is the most attractive man I’ve ever seen with enough charisma to blind the sun.</p> <p>He’s bigger than the world, owns half of it, and conquered the other half.</p> <p>He was forbidden. Wrong.</p> <p>So I totally got over him. Or so I told myself.</p> <p>Until we’re forced to get married.</p> <p>Now I’m trapped.</p> <p>But maybe he’s trapped too.</p> <p>Because we’re both reaching for that forbidden fruit dangling between us.</p> <p><i>Empire of Desire</i> is a complete stand-alone. No other books should be listened to prior to this.</p>"; 
